## ğŸ“Œ Overview
This is a PHP-based online learning and productivity platform developed as a group project.  
It includes modules for learning, quizzes, to-do task management, user authentication, admin control, and a simple chatbot.  
The project also includes Docker support and a basic CI/CD structure.

